properties.name: rabbit.supplier.requeue
properties.description: Whether rejected messages should be requeued.

properties.name: rabbit.supplier.queues
properties.description: The queues to which the source will listen for messages.

properties.name: rabbit.supplier.initialRetryInterval
properties.description: Initial retry interval when retry is enabled.

properties.name: rabbit.supplier.maxRetryInterval
properties.description: Max retry interval when retry is enabled.

properties.name: rabbit.supplier.retryMultiplier
properties.description: Retry backoff multiplier when retry is enabled.

properties.name: rabbit.supplier.maxAttempts
properties.description: The maximum delivery attempts when retry is enabled.

properties.name: rabbit.supplier.ownConnection
properties.description: When true, use a separate connection based on the boot properties.
